  <steps>
    <step num="0">Heat oil in a large pot over medium-high heat. </step>
    <step num="1">Cook chorizo until slightly crispy. </step>
    <step num="2">Add the onions and cook until translucent. </step>
    <step num="3">Add the beef, salt, and pepper, cooking until no pink is showing. </step>
    <step num="4">Pour in the tomato sauce, and cook until sauce thickens. </step>
